casebody.data:
No. 10-8590 (10A737). Emmanuel Fitzgerald Hammond, Petitioner v. Brian Owens, Commissioner, Georgia Department of Corrections, et al. 562 U.S. 1208, 131 S. Ct. 1067,

178 L. Ed. 2d 881,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 1073. January 25, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Georgia, Fulton County, denied. The order heretofore entered by Justice Thomas vacated.
